English: I got ammo, someone else carry this!

Spanish.Translation: Tengo munición, ¡que se lo quede otro!

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Tenho munição, alguém pode pegar esta!

Polish.Translation: Mam amunicję, niech weźmie to ktoś inny!

Japanese.Translation: 弾薬だ。誰か運んでくれ！

Korean.Translation: 나한테 탄약 있어. 누가 이것 좀 들어!

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 我有彈藥，誰來拿著這個！

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 我有弹药，其他人拿这个！
